switchTopCellAndLefSet(25.10)                    switchTopCellAndLefSet(25.10)

Name
       switchTopCellAndLefSet

Syntax
       switchTopCellAndLefSet

       [-help]

       [<cellName>]

       Switches  the top cell to specified die name, and switches current tech
       lib to the relative die tech lib.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs a brief description that includes type and  default  in-
              formation for each switchTopCellAndLefSet parameter.

       <cellName>
              Specifies the top cell name.

